{
  "_meta": {
    "name": "MCMP Chatbot",
    "description": "Visual abstraction of the MCMP Chatbot (mcmp_chatbot repo): Leopold LLM agent with MCP tools querying JSON data files and an institutional graph, plus a scraper orchestrator pipeline that keeps the data fresh.",
